---
title: Creamy Mushroom Stroganoff with Spinach and Speedy Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Mushroom Stroganoff in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mushroom-stroganoff-cea7677f-1a973461.jpg
